{"title":"舰队继续远航（外一章）","authors":["苏叔阳"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":7,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"舰队继续远航（外一章）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏叔阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的老船长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熄灭了他心脏的炉火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将自己溶入了海洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他将眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍重地留在世上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让所有的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分享他智慧的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他对人民深情的挚爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻写在每座山岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他未了的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注入后继者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的胸膛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经融进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民大会堂里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林般的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的规划"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经印在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的航海图上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不息的长风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹动每片树叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗哗作响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的期盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不灭的星光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着每粒石子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熠熠闪亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们桅杆上的彩旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄傲地飞扬着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他崇高的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的汽笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奏响《义勇军进行曲》的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高亢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的指挥员们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧起老船长的海图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站好了自己的岗位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臂膀连着臂膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东为我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破了坚冰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平给我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明确了航向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新一代的领航员们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经将历史的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接力棒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严地握在手掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百年翻腾的烈焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不曾烧毁遍野的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血与火的锻造"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锤打出民族前进的悲壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们民族文明的核燃料"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经点燃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动力舱里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉火正旺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个水手的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都凝望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥舱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威武的舰队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集合起几辈人的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝结成无比的坚强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩荡荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈波斩浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续远航远航"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接挑战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我这个病残的歌者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾同死亡擦肩而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我愉快而自豪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我属于一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在千灾百难中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不颓丧的中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外面的世界有万种风情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但风情万种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不属于我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有我迷恋的爱情的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我梦里醉醒的爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有比我祖父更老更老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比我的孩子更年轻更年轻的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的每一根白发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都充盈着一段苦涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我的黑眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天都复印着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更美丽的黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不敢确定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是否能越过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本世纪的门槛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我的耳朵已经听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这强壮的新世纪的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听啊听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在向我们召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让虚夸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥霍了热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让贪婪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞吃了忠诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让腐败"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锈蚀了灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要让骄奢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫荡了光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要为了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘取富裕的金苹果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮躁到抓住气球升空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要因为十步的顺利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盲目了脚下的路程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是又一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前人未曾经历的事业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要的是悲壮的勇敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热烈的清醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有数千年文明根基的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是青翠了历史的大树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是漂泊的浮萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游走在岁月的掌心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不是听任轻薄的旋风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随意吹动的流云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装扮我们的壮美生命的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅仅是珠宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅仅是黄金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上最闪光的是真理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有真理照耀的富有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是片暗淡的黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当五星红旗和紫荆花旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拉手飞上蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意味着不可追回的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们发起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后的挑战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将向我们聚焦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我们是否能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"协调稳步地向前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我最钟爱的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我最心疼的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起我们世代相传"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捶打不折的腰杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起漫天蔽日的大旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接明天的挑战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（选自长诗《世纪之歌》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}